task.summary: Reorganizing this repository to contain the latest version of the standard Android Server application that is distributed to Platypus customers (non-madara version).
Restored winch fixes from different branch. Small changes suggested by static code analysis.
Updated crwlib_core.jar to the most up to date code base and updated SensorType enum for new sensors. Started cleaning up sensor parsing and adding temperature compensation for DO and pH sensors.
